    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 14.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第14课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Do You Speak English?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你会讲英语吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Did the young man speak English?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那个年轻人会讲英语吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "I had an amusing experience last year.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "去年我有过一次有趣的经历。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "After I had left a small village in the south of France, I drove on to the next town.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "离开法国南部的一个小村庄后，我继续驶往下一个城镇。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "On the way, a young man waved to me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "途中，一个年轻人向我挥手。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "I stopped and he asked me for a lift.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我停下车，他请求搭车。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "As soon as he had got into the car, I said good morning to him in French, and he replied in the same language.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他一上车，我就用法语向他道早安，他也用同样的语言回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Apart from a few words, I do not know any French at all.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "除了个别词以外，我完全不懂法语。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Neither of us spoke during the journey.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "旅途中我们谁也没有说话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "I had nearly reached the town when the young man suddenly said very slowly, Do you speak English?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "快到城里时，那年轻人突然慢慢地说：“你会讲英语吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "As I soon learnt, he was English himself.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我很快便知道，他自己就是英国人。"
      }
    }
  ],
